title: DIAMOND RUSH
description:
DIAMOND RUSH

*Diamond Rush - The most popular adventure game of your old cellphone is now available on the store!
Grab the diamonds and take to your heels!
*An uneasy adventure is in prospect for you: Tibetan stalactites falling from above, thick Angora forests, poisonous spiders of Bavarian castle and other vicissitudes of life will accompany your every step.
*Tons of different obstacles and traps to get around: deadly spiders, bone-crushing rocks, malicious knights, falling ice, snakes, etc
